Languages.Title: Google Analytics 4 (GA4)
Languages.Description:
Google Analytics 4 (GA4) is a web analytics tool developed by Google that collects metrics and insights on how your customers browse and use your websites.

Our integrations tracks GA4 events on your Members Portal such as page visits, items added to cart, and more! You can then use these events metrics in GA4 to improve your Members Portal performance and user experience.
